snippet.title: SolSeraph | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
SolSeraph descends onto the PlayStation 4, Xbox One, Nintendo Switch, and Steam for PC on July 10 for $14.99! SolSeraph puts you in the wing-tipped shoes of an almighty divinity who is tasked with rebuilding civilization while protecting the populace from the constant threat of mythical demons and monsters!

Official website: https://www.sol-seraph.com/
